Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們釘釘子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊這麼順利呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 這種時候不冷靜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想不到好主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主意 主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮家裡 廁所門上不是有個把手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個怎麼看都像隻鴨子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 夏夏想到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越用力想 越是什麼都想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼新奇的主意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非夏夏 真的覺得我什麼都沒想到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我一直在裝沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是開個玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜歡思考這種尖端科技了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是折刀的刀柄部分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 自信爆表啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者 如果妳叫我『會走路的活字典』我會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活字典本來就會走路的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我來劃線做標記
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏夏用鋸子沿線鋸木板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋸完之後要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按我說的順序釘上釘子固定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先用那塊板作為底座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那塊大板立起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中間一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右邊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這是小蓮想出來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連我都覺得做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮 這是用來做什麼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我現在就用一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要睡覺啊 很令人困擾！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 最後做成這樣了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 書架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這氣味…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是咖哩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我要開始上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校的咖哩和蓮華…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個組合…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過蓮華應該不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做夢也想不到本校會發生那種大悲劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下課啦 下課啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去玩積木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能把娃娃帶到學校呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生沒問題呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上課的時候是收起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被老師看到的話要沒收的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師說過上課的時候不要玩就沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 今天日影休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明昨天還是活蹦亂跳的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 今天的午餐是咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影那份也可以吃掉了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 好歹稍微關心一下日影呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那木實就只有一份咖哩了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行 我也很想多吃咖哩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曹操到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來得好晚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了點麻煩事所以遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姊 遲到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不~行呀 不~行呀 我~要告訴老~師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是小孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姊背著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:11:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影 學校不准帶那種東西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被老師看到的話要沒收的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔喔 在動呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們把我家妹妹當成什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母發燒去醫院了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我在學校照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才遲到了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話請假不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的午餐是咖哩 所以不能請假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呿 竟然記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼賣點心的 給
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師說了 年紀最大的賣點心的要負責照顧蓮華
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀 這種事情木實更適合做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算妳這麼說 決定好的事情也不會改了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了喔大姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂木實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來來 小夏和小鞠一起來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛君也過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要逃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 抱抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我抱也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會哄小孩子 真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華見到有興趣的東西就會咬喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是很好嗎 她很喜歡妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濕答答的 我要去洗一下校服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華的奶嘴掉在地上了 我也要去洗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要創造積木高度的新紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那兩個人把小孩丟下跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 這孩子已經會走路了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的過來了呀 好可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏海的最高紀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的最高紀錄…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的最高紀錄…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只剩下一塊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 一點小事哭什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家之後我把點心分妳一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是姊姊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害呢 小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經三年級了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點小事當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生小吉先生 小吉先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生濕答答了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鞠冷靜點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了怎麼了 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了很多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華她… 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明剛才還在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非去走廊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走廊裡沒看見呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進配膳室了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是叫人操心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是主菜桶 妳準備對咖哩做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華把咖哩當成人質… 咖哩質了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華 Stop Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家好期待的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩咖哩咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待很久的咖哩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩咖哩咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 小蓮第一次上學就把學校鎮壓下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法忘記那個瞬間呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親戚送的梨子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞌睡防止裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是蓮華做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個要怎麼用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:15:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打掃差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書得放好才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛 踩到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那是什麼呀 彈力球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是彈力球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像比以前更破了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破成這樣不能要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫忙找一下我的彈力球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踩到的話會很痛 所以要小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那表情怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和體檢完之後的表情一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我踩到妳的彈力球了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隨便跑進我的房間玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來在那裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是寶物的話為什麼會丟在我的房間呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是丟在這
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是剛好找到以前喜歡的彈力球 丟著玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不還是在丟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 接下來要做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要把書收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相冊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼時候的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很老的照片了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過為什麼我臉上有傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得是小吉先生掉到門外 去撿的時候摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳好學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 沒預先聯絡就過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 外面很熱呢 進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢好像做了不少我的布娃娃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地上什麼都沒有卻摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對… 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自做的那些布娃娃果然還是很糟糕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不糟糕呀 做得很好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候喜歡的娃娃變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓妳教我怎麼樣把它補好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁 裁縫工具在我的房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可以進螢的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也帶了裁縫工具過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個 學姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了這麼多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢真的很喜歡娃娃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這方面很像個小學生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過呀 也不要只做我的娃娃 做點其他人的娃娃怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都做一樣的很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不會無聊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這個娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣才能補好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經破得很厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是覺得用新布重新做一個可能會更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話就會變成另一個娃娃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要縫補丁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 那裡應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢做得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姊 沒事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走了 螢下次來我家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊 吃晚餐了 來拿餐具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 那個彈力球怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放回壁櫥的玩具箱裡面了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心不要再丟掉了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然後悔也沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼突然學起大人說話來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:21:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大人了呀
